title: #005 - Just Dave Van Ronk (Dave Van Ronk)
description:
#005 is Just Dave Van Ronk under West-Indie catalog, originally released in 1964.


Review	by Richard Meyer

This collection is comprised of solo guitar and vocal interpretations of blues and traditional standards. Van Ronk&#039;s understated guitar style is perfect for these intimate performances. His naturally rough voice allows him to sing these songs believably without any ethnic affectation or false energy.

4/5 ****
